00:15:47,400 --> 00:15:48,960
After all these years,

285
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:52,240
they have already treated you as their own daughter.

286
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:55,160
If Mr. Jiang saw you like this,

287
00:15:55,680 --> 00:15:57,440
he would hug you

288
00:15:57,800 --> 00:15:59,460
and persuade you to turn back.

289
00:15:59,800 --> 00:16:01,440
I let them down.

290
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:03,240
He won't come.

291
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:05,160
You are wrong.

292
00:16:05,520 --> 00:16:07,040
They all love you.

293
00:16:07,320 --> 00:16:08,760
For those who love you,

294
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:10,560
stop it.

295
00:16:12,640 --> 00:16:13,520
Hurry up and save them.

296
00:16:13,520 --> 00:16:14,360
Hurry.

297
00:16:14,360 --> 00:16:15,680
The one I held at that moment,

298
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:17,120
though a murderer,

299
00:16:17,520 --> 00:16:20,120
was also a poor soul swallowed by darkness.

300
00:16:20,760 --> 00:16:21,760
We got them!

301
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:23,080
Come up quickly.

302
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:25,240
Eight years ago,

303
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:29,080
we lost our child.

304
00:16:30,680 --> 00:16:32,520
Her mother went mad.

305
00:16:32,920 --> 00:16:34,600
Siyan, if you are not good,

306
00:16:34,640 --> 00:16:35,840
Mommy will be angry.

307
00:16:37,400 --> 00:16:38,840
Good Siyan.

308
00:16:39,720 --> 00:16:42,600
Good Siyan. The doctor suggested I raise the foundling

309
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:44,400
as Jiang Siyan.

310
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:48,200
This might help alleviate her mother's illness.

311
00:16:49,760 --> 00:16:51,090
After thinking it over,

312
00:16:52,800 --> 00:16:55,560
this might be the best choice.

313
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:01,880
I took her back,

314
00:17:02,440 --> 00:17:04,560
forged a fake notice,

315
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:09,319
and lied that she was our lost daughter,

316
00:17:09,560 --> 00:17:10,720
Jiang Siyan.

317
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:12,880
Child,

318
00:17:13,640 --> 00:17:15,770
do you remember everything I told you?

319
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:18,599
What is your name?

320
00:17:18,599 --> 00:17:20,280
Jiang Siyan. I'm 10 years old.

321
00:17:20,319 --> 00:17:22,119
I got lost making sugar skewers.

322
00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:24,760
Good child.

323
00:17:25,079 --> 00:17:26,940
Come, Dad will take you to see Mom.

324
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:32,280
Siyan, it's getting cold.

325
00:17:32,520 --> 00:17:35,040
Mom will make you a pretty floral dress.

326
00:17:37,240 --> 00:17:39,720
Dear, look who's here.

327
00:17:39,840 --> 00:17:41,170
Look who I brought back.

328
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,840
I found our daughter.

329
00:17:46,640 --> 00:17:47,920
Siyan, come closer.

330
00:17:47,960 --> 00:17:49,560
Let Mom get a good look at you.

331
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:52,400
No.

332
00:17:53,120 --> 00:17:54,480
She is not my daughter.

333
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:56,120
She is not my daughter.

334
00:17:57,640 --> 00:17:59,760
Siyan, hurry, call her Mom.

335
00:18:00,280 --> 00:18:02,040
Mom, I am Siyan.

336
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:04,640
Go away.

337
00:18:04,680 --> 00:18:05,680
My Siyan

338
00:18:06,040 --> 00:18:07,160
My Siyan

339
00:18:08,440 --> 00:18:09,760
doesn't look like this.

340
00:18:09,760 --> 00:18:10,840
It's not like this.

341
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:12,880
No.

342
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:12,880
Dear, look.

343
00:18:13,040 --> 00:18:15,000
Isn't this our daughter Siyan?

344
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:19,240
Look how much she resembles her.

345
00:18:19,320 --> 00:18:20,720
This is our daughter.

346
00:18:20,720 --> 00:18:20,880
[Missing Person Notice]

347
00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:21,720
[Missing Person Notice]

348
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:21,920
[Missing Person Notice]

349
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:23,000
Mom, you asked me to learn to make sugar skewers.

350
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:24,320
Mom, you asked me to learn to make sugar skewers.

351
00:18:24,320 --> 00:18:25,720
Come back early after you're done.

352
00:18:25,720 --> 00:18:27,200
I also said I would bring you a skewer

353
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:28,640
to see if it's sweet.

354
00:18:33,360 --> 00:18:35,960
Right.

355
00:18:35,960 --> 00:18:36,160
[Missing Person Notice]

356
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:37,690
Come, hurry up and tell Mom.

357
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:39,440
What did you do the day it rained?

358
00:18:39,440 --> 00:18:40,680
It rained that day.

359
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:41,680
I got lost

360
00:18:41,720 --> 00:18:43,200
and lost my shoes.

361
00:18:43,840 --> 00:18:45,400
Let Mom see.

362
00:18:45,440 --> 00:18:46,600
Why aren't you wearing shoes?

363
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:47,320
Are you cold?

364
00:18:47,320 --> 00:18:48,680
Where are your shoes?

365
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:51,960
Dear, I found her shoes.

366
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,600
Let Mom put them on you.

367
00:19:07,200 --> 00:19:08,400
They are on.

368
00:19:08,600 --> 00:19:10,200
They are on.

369
00:19:15,240 --> 00:19:16,480
Mom, is it sweet?

370
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:22,840
Sweet, very sweet.

371
00:19:24,520 --> 00:19:25,320
Siyan.

372
00:19:26,440 --> 00:19:27,880
My daughter.

373
00:19:27,920 --> 00:19:30,520
Where did you run off to?

374
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:34,720
Mom couldn't find you anywhere.

375
00:19:34,960 --> 00:19:36,120
Don't run off anymore.

376
00:19:36,120 --> 00:19:37,480
You mustn't run away.

377
00:19:40,600 --> 00:19:42,160
Don't run off.

378
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:44,960
Mr. Jiang.

379
00:19:45,760 --> 00:19:47,040
Based on what you said,

380
00:19:47,400 --> 00:19:50,530
the real Jiang Siyan was very likely murdered back then.

381
00:19:53,320 --> 00:19:56,120
I happen to have the skeleton of a little girl here.

382
00:19:56,160 --> 00:19:57,720
The pelvis is relatively narrow,

383
00:19:57,720 --> 00:19:59,680
identifying it as a female child.

384
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:01,960
Based on the weathering

385
00:20:02,040 --> 00:20:04,200
and color changes of the bones,

386
00:20:04,320 --> 00:20:06,920
the time of death is estimated to be 8 years ago.

387
00:20:09,040 --> 00:20:10,720
Do you want to identify it?

388
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:53,800
The style of these clothes.

389
00:20:54,480 --> 00:20:56,680
It belongs to my daughter, Siyan.

390
00:20:57,480 --> 00:20:58,440
I remember

391
00:20:58,760 --> 00:21:01,880
she was wearing these clothes when she left.

392
00:21:06,520 --> 00:21:07,640
This one isn't.

393
00:21:08,600 --> 00:21:10,520
My daughter doesn't have this one.

394
00:21:10,520 --> 00:21:11,960
Siyan doesn't have it.

395
00:21:16,520 --> 00:21:18,000
Siyan,

396
00:21:18,040 --> 00:21:20,160
who killed you?

397
00:21:23,560 --> 00:21:24,240
Lord Li,

398
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:26,320
Lord Li, I beg you.

399
00:21:26,360 --> 00:21:27,280
Tell me,

400
00:21:27,360 --> 00:21:29,440
is this my daughter Siyan?

401
00:21:29,800 --> 00:21:31,760
Who killed her?

402
00:21:32,840 --> 00:21:34,320
You must catch the killer

403
00:21:34,360 --> 00:21:36,440
and avenge my daughter.

404
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:38,200
I beg you.

405
00:21:38,240 --> 00:21:38,920
Mr. Jiang.

406
00:21:38,240 --> 00:21:38,920
I beg you.

407
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:40,840
Mr. Jiang, please get up. I beg you to catch the killer.

408
00:21:40,840 --> 00:21:41,640
Mr. Jiang.

409
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,080
My daughter,

410
00:21:47,040 --> 00:21:49,200
I'm taking you home.

411
00:21:49,480 --> 00:21:50,480
Rest assured.

412
00:21:52,320 --> 00:21:54,320
I will definitely catch the killer.

413
00:22:05,280 --> 00:22:06,960
Don't rush.

414
00:22:05,280 --> 00:22:06,960
I want some too.

415
00:22:07,120 --> 00:22:08,480
There's enough for everyone.

416
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:09,210
Don't choke.

417
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:10,440
Drink slowly.

418
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:10,440
Thank you.

419
00:22:10,720 --> 00:22:11,880
Thank you, ma'am.

420
00:22:11,920 --> 00:22:13,320
Don't push. There's more.

421
00:22:13,320 --> 00:22:14,520
Thank you, ma'am.

422
00:22:15,560 --> 00:22:16,690
I want another bowl.

423
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:17,400
Okay.

424
00:22:18,240 --> 00:22:18,920
Here.

425
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:20,320
So delicious.

426
00:22:20,360 --> 00:22:21,690
Who are you looking for?

427
00:22:23,600 --> 00:22:25,480
You work with Constable Narisu.

428
00:22:26,360 --> 00:22:27,600
I'm here for Jueming.

429
00:22:27,840 --> 00:22:29,900
Did that brat get into trouble again?

430
00:22:30,560 --> 00:22:31,280
No.

431
00:22:31,840 --> 00:22:32,760
Not at all.

432
00:22:33,120 --> 00:22:35,480
I just came to talk to him about a case.

433
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:37,160
You scared me.

434
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:38,000
Have a seat.

435
00:22:38,080 --> 00:22:39,040
He'll be back in a while.

436
00:22:39,040 --> 00:22:39,800
Alright.

437
00:22:42,280 --> 00:22:43,410
Thank you. Drink up.

438
00:22:44,080 --> 00:22:45,740
You haven't got any, have you?

439
00:22:50,120 --> 00:22:51,440
Is this his room?

440
00:22:54,600 --> 00:22:56,560
This mustard greens porridge is Jueming's favorite.

441
00:22:56,560 --> 00:22:57,820
Do you want to try some?

442
00:22:58,040 --> 00:22:59,400
Sure, thanks.

443
00:23:02,160 --> 00:23:02,760
Here.

444
00:23:04,560 --> 00:23:05,560
It's delicious.

445
00:23:15,160 --> 00:23:16,360
Here, have a taste.

446
00:23:17,600 --> 00:23:18,320
Thank you.

447
00:23:21,120 --> 00:23:22,320
Drink slowly too.

448
00:23:22,360 --> 00:23:23,840
Don't choke.

449
00:23:22,360 --> 00:23:23,840
Mmm.

450
00:23:27,120 --> 00:23:28,050
It's delicious.

451
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:29,440
No wonder they like it.

452
00:23:29,760 --> 00:23:32,200
The osmanthus cake I make is also Jueming's favorite.

453
00:23:32,200 --> 00:23:33,530
You can try it next time.

454
00:23:38,440 --> 00:23:40,560
Has he lived here since he was a child?

455
00:23:44,960 --> 00:23:48,200
I really feel for the boy Jueming.

456
00:23:49,280 --> 00:23:50,480
When he was seven,

457
00:23:50,760 --> 00:23:52,280
his mother was murdered in the pharmacy.

458
00:23:52,280 --> 00:23:54,410
The case remains unsolved to this day.

459
00:23:54,880 --> 00:23:56,940
Jueming became an orphan after that,

460
00:23:56,960 --> 00:23:58,840
and had to work at such a young age.

461
00:23:59,800 --> 00:24:01,040
I felt sorry for him,

462
00:24:01,280 --> 00:24:02,880
so I let him stay in the backyard

463
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:04,640
to sweep the courtyard.

464
00:24:05,320 --> 00:24:07,200
But Jueming is also a smart boy.

465
00:24:07,840 --> 00:24:08,800
Once,

466
00:24:09,120 --> 00:24:11,600
Miss Xianglan gave him some pastries she made.

467
00:24:11,600 --> 00:24:12,480
Jueming.

468
00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:14,260
Eat something.

469
00:24:20,800 --> 00:24:21,600
Xianglan,

470
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:25,920
The wealthy Merchant Ma you usually entertain is not a merchant,

471
00:24:25,920 --> 00:24:27,160
but a scholar.

472
00:24:28,320 --> 00:24:29,480
How do you know?

473
00:24:33,600 --> 00:24:34,860
He has a childish face,

474
00:24:35,280 --> 00:24:38,120
and there are ink stains on the pads of his index and middle fingers.

475
00:24:38,120 --> 00:24:40,440
He usually likes to show you his poetry collections.

476
00:24:40,440 --> 00:24:41,640
His family must be strict,

477
00:24:41,640 --> 00:24:42,640
valuing reputation,

478
00:24:42,640 --> 00:24:43,960
and fearing criticism.

479
00:24:43,960 --> 00:24:45,800
You just need to praise his poems,

480
00:24:45,800 --> 00:24:47,000
and he will be happy.

481
00:24:47,800 --> 00:24:49,400
He was actually right.

482
00:24:49,840 --> 00:24:52,240
Xianglan received a lot of tips since then.

483
00:24:52,600 --> 00:24:53,840
After this spread,

484
00:24:54,280 --> 00:24:56,000
Jueming became the most popular person

485
00:24:56,000 --> 00:24:57,440
in Yichun Brothel.

486
00:25:00,480 --> 00:25:02,600
However, the tips the girls gave him,

487
00:25:02,640 --> 00:25:04,160
he saved them every time.

488
00:25:05,080 --> 00:25:06,400
I only found out today

489
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:09,800
that he wanted to buy back the old pharmacy.

490
00:25:11,120 --> 00:25:11,800
The pharmacy?

491
00:25:11,800 --> 00:25:12,480
Yeah.

492
00:25:12,600 --> 00:25:14,880
Do you know where the pharmacy is?

493
00:25:15,040 --> 00:25:16,040
Of course.

494
00:25:16,360 --> 00:25:18,960
Is there any place in Luoyang that I don't know?

495
00:25:26,880 --> 00:25:28,840
Oh, this house

496
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:31,010
has been lived in by several families.

497
00:25:31,120 --> 00:25:31,840
You

498
00:25:32,240 --> 00:25:34,280
are quite sentimental about your home.

499
00:25:34,280 --> 00:25:35,740
You saved money for so long

500
00:25:35,880 --> 00:25:37,560
just to redeem this house.

501
00:25:44,120 --> 00:25:44,920
Give me the land deed.

502
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:45,850
What's the rush?

503
00:25:46,040 --> 00:25:47,080
Did you bring enough money?

504
00:25:47,080 --> 00:25:47,760
Enough.

505
00:25:58,200 --> 00:26:00,480
It was this price a few years ago.

506
00:26:00,680 --> 00:26:02,800
But now, it's more than that.

507
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:05,480
Didn't we agree?

508
00:26:05,920 --> 00:26:06,920
I give you eight taels of silver,

509
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:08,520
and you give me the land deed?

510
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:09,450
Back then...

511
00:26:09,720 --> 00:26:12,080
Back then, it was because no one wanted this house.

512
00:26:12,080 --> 00:26:13,440
Look, so many years have passed.

513
00:26:13,440 --> 00:26:14,560
I've put a lot of effort into it,

514
00:26:14,560 --> 00:26:16,040
and finally someone moved in.

515
00:26:16,040 --> 00:26:18,440
I informed you right after they moved out.

516
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:21,120
If it's inconvenient for you,

517
00:26:21,840 --> 00:26:23,900
I'll just put the house on the market.

518
00:26:25,120 --> 00:26:25,840
Wait.

519
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:30,680
How much do you want now?

520
00:26:33,800 --> 00:26:34,680
Twenty taels.

521
00:26:35,080 --> 00:26:36,120
Twenty taels?

522
00:26:36,560 --> 00:26:38,440
This isn't a price increase.

523
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:39,800
This is extortion!

524
00:26:41,120 --> 00:26:42,050
Why are you here?

525
00:26:43,560 --> 00:26:44,600
This lady

526
00:26:44,840 --> 00:26:46,640
looks like a wealthy one.

527
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:47,920
Good eye.

528
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:49,440
Show me the land deed.

529
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:54,400
If you don't show it to me,

530
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:56,320
how do I know this house is yours?

531
00:27:02,080 --> 00:27:02,800
What are you doing?

532
00:27:02,800 --> 00:27:03,680
Robbing the land deed!

533
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:05,480
Robbery! Robbery!

534
00:27:05,520 --> 00:27:07,580
Don't come closer! Give it back to me.

535
00:27:07,920 --> 00:27:10,080
Stop yelling!

536
00:27:26,960 --> 00:27:27,880
This purse

537
00:27:28,280 --> 00:27:29,080
is mine now.

538
00:27:29,320 --> 00:27:29,960
Too much, right?

539
00:27:29,960 --> 00:27:30,960
Enough, enough.

540
00:27:32,120 --> 00:27:33,920
Then this house is yours.

541
00:27:34,440 --> 00:27:35,160
Farewell.

542
00:27:36,160 --> 00:27:37,280
Wait.

543
00:27:38,160 --> 00:27:40,620
Don't you want your mother's pharmacy back?

544
00:27:41,800 --> 00:27:43,060
You saw Sister Chunyi?

545
00:27:43,880 --> 00:27:44,560
I...

546
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:49,080
Look, he has the house deed.

547
00:27:49,120 --> 00:27:50,640
He can raise the price however he wants.

548
00:27:50,640 --> 00:27:54,000
Besides, housing prices in Luoyang keep going up.

549
00:27:54,040 --> 00:27:56,600
You definitely can't save money that fast.

550
00:28:03,720 --> 00:28:05,200
You paid for it. It's yours.

551
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:06,520
Wait.

552
00:28:06,720 --> 00:28:08,380
I haven't finished speaking.

553
00:28:09,640 --> 00:28:10,920
Let's make a deal.

554
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:16,000
Come to the yamen and help me investigate cases

555
00:28:16,240 --> 00:28:18,080
to pay off your debt.

556
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:20,320
I see that you

557
00:28:20,360 --> 00:28:21,440
have a clear mind

558
00:28:21,480 --> 00:28:23,480
and are suited for investigating cases.

559
00:28:23,480 --> 00:28:24,840
You're full of talent.

560
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:26,160
As for your looks,

561
00:28:27,040 --> 00:28:28,370
you're quite ordinary.

562
00:28:29,160 --> 00:28:30,640
Perfect for our yamen.

563
00:28:31,440 --> 00:28:32,640
I heard

564
00:28:33,280 --> 00:28:34,920
the allowance for a constable in the yamen

565
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:36,640
is about ten taels a year.

566
00:28:37,360 --> 00:28:38,220
How about this?

567
00:28:38,600 --> 00:28:39,760
I'll help you solve cases.

568
00:28:39,760 --> 00:28:40,880
Two taels per case.

569
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:44,920
Here is ten taels.

570
00:28:45,760 --> 00:28:46,840
After five cases,

571
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:48,140
the house deed is mine.

572
00:28:48,360 --> 00:28:49,200
Deal.

573
00:28:49,840 --> 00:28:51,100
Hold onto this for now.

574
